Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 外面有一位来客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自称是主公旧友许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请求拜见主公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是袁绍帐下的许攸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下不知 那人只说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公应该记得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当年偷鸡宰鹅之事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}穿鞋呀 主公 丞相 丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}穿鞋呀 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相穿上鞋子 快快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}南阳故人许攸 叩见孟德公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么会到这儿来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍不能相容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我如再不来投
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐性命难保啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是天下掉下来一座金山呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我得兄台相助 大事可成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受我一拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不敢 不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄请起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄 高义呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忘履相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着实令在下受宠若惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}见到你许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我岂能不得意忘形吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走走走 进去说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说说吧 为何来投我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我曾给袁绍献一计
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他集四十万大军 分作两路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一路十万人马 佯攻你的大营
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另一路集三十万精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}径取许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我告诉袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论这两路人马哪路能够得手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你曹孟德都将大败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍果真如此用兵 我必亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惜呀 忠言逆耳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庸主非但不听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反而要寄下我这颗项上的头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}留作他日后问罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}良臣事庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真乃人生莫大的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此妙计 袁绍怎么会不用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍他认为你诡计多端
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你连堂堂的大汉天子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都能用来行骗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂不会设下伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诱使我们去偷袭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世人都说我多疑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来还有人比我更多疑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你已经把他们给吓怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恕许攸直言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实你曹孟德远没有那么强大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可恰恰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是那些庸人心目中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对你的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不仅助长而且成就了你的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}精辟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}除了你许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我永远也听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么精彩的褒奖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}越是精辟之言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就越有杀身之祸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实在是无奈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天我才转投于你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如孟德兄不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今以后 许攸愿效犬马之劳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄台呀 你早就该来投我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这天底下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有我能配得上你的满腹才华
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}容我问你一事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还望你能够如实相告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你我现在已经是同舟共济
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是荣辱与共的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我任何事情都不会瞒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你军中的粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尚可支撑多少时日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄台果然是高人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一问就问到了我的痛处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我此次出征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原本带了百日军粮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不料耗损巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在还有五十日的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未必吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟旁人是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是实际上还有一个月的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可悲呀 我许攸冒死前来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诚心相投
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原以为是弃暗投明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你根本不相信我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵法云 兵不厌诈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可千万不要泄露出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}免得乱了我的军心哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我目前只有十日的军粮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹孟德啊 曹孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难怪世人都说你是奸雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来 他们都太低俗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本就不了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我认为你是奸雄之祖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}古今无双 空前绝后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹孟德 你根本没有十日之粮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}言重了 言重了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我无非
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是问问你军中粮草的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可你前前后后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}转瞬之间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就跟我撒了三次谎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你根本就没有十日之粮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:09:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 什么事都瞒不过你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我就给你透个实情儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我现在还剩五日的粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我正为此焦虑万分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫非你还要骗我第四次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此话怎讲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你连隔日之粮都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你军中已经断粮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从明天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你和你的军士将杀马充饥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我截获了你催要军粮的军令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可他知道有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他根本就不信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他认定以你曹孟德的精明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绝不会在临战之际断粮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他更不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你曹孟德断了粮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然还不退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此 他必然认定你没有断粮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我现在军中只剩半日之粮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我唯一的指望就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天日落时分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军粮能如期送到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果明日运不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若是我许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}送给你百万石粮草 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那袁绍所有的辎重粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全部屯于乌巢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乌巢的守军相当薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}守将淳于琼 那是个酒囊饭袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不堪重用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你能亲率一只铁骑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连夜杀奔乌巢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一把火烧了他的辎重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁军势必大乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也可顺势
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夺取你所需要的粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我会亲自率军前去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有一事想问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就不怕我许攸说的是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍早已经在乌巢设下伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个我不担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是袁绍 更非庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的假的 我闻得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何以见得呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其一 我一直苦思不解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍为何兵败了还不退军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且能在短短十几日之内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就能重新召回几十万残军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来他手里有吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}残军不回营 就得饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其二 你许攸深夜来投我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必有大礼相送
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄台不愧是天下明主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今往后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我若能服侍明主 如同再造
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幸甚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我灭了袁绍 你是头功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄 你打算何时启程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事不宜退 我这就出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会率猛将十员 精骑五千
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奔袭乌巢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}估计会在黎明时分到达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 如此甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄 一定切记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在你奔袭途中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如遇袁兵 不必与其纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只须亮出袁军的旗号即可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就称是后将军蒋奇的兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是奉袁绍之命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驰援乌巢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢兄台指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁军的旗甲我倒是缴获了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚正好可以用上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还是吃不准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果乌巢一旦火起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍会当如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍定会火速派兵救援乌巢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍这个人平时虽然昏庸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可一旦圣明起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}往往也能做出让人意外的事来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他势必置乌巢于不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}集中所有兵马直扑你的大营
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他一定会认为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你曹孟德率轻骑 奔了乌巢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的大营势必空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 还是兄台更了解袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 在下建议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你必须留下一支兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在大营之外设下伏击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在大营之外设下埋伏 不 这样太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 这样太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会把我的空营丢给他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}径直去取他的官渡大营
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要知道袁绍的大营
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可比我的大营大多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放火 给我烧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公有令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用乌巢的军车运粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 把粮包装上车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 不好了 乌巢起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 乌巢起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么 哪儿起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}西北方 乌巢起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坏了 坏了 坏了 坏了 坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快快快 我的天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坏了 坏了 坏了 坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操我非要掘你的祖坟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操你夜袭乌巢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我百万军粮毁于一炬呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 这曹贼一定没有走远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们赶紧驰援乌巢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 乌巢粮械一旦被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}营中只剩三日军粮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大军不能久持啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如挥师追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与曹操决一死战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 决一死战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慌什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不就是那几屯粮草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我四十万大军俱在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操奈何我也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请父帅下令 我们如何应战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们想想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乌巢有八千守军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顷刻间化为乌有 这说明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操的所有精锐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都已经去奔袭乌巢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操的大营空虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 传令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弃乌巢不顾 赶紧调集兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由我亲自带领前往曹操大营
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁军来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁军来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你中了我们的埋伏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快快下马受死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弟兄们 放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹军有埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快快传令 撤回官渡大营
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公 主公 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操趁我军不备 攻袭我军大营
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操趁我军不备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}攻袭我军大营
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操 我和你不共戴天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公 父帅 父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们跟曹操决一死战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}决一死战吧父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下令吧 父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 撤军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回冀州
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撤军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 撤军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸降曹了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们的乌巢被焚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大营丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全是这个贼给害的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}高览 张郃 及诸位将士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汝等且听我一言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你家主公袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生性优柔寡断 刚愎自用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤愚不分 忠奸不明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}似这等庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安有不败之理乎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有 他那三位公子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,0:22:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁谭 袁熙 袁尚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既无胸怀大志 且自私贪婪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了争夺世子大位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却忘了纲常礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:22:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不讲手足之情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你争我夺 勾心斗角
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.12,0:23:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早晚必反目成仇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定有一场血光之灾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尔等如果再迁延不决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大难必将临头了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}古人云
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}良禽择木而栖 良臣择主而侍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听我一言 列位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尔等还不如效仿我许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悬岸勒马 当机立断
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弃暗投明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家想叛我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如叛我 现在就刺我一枪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿我的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:23:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}献给曹操领功去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如不叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我令你们立刻上山 砍杀许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 山上肯定有伏军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时上山 这 等于是送死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为将者 岂能贪生怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.75,0:24:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冲上去 我令你们冲上去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.53,0:24:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 有伏军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.40,0:24:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.15,0:25:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快撤 快撤 撤
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.71,0:25:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们还有多少人马
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.19,0:25:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀父帅 不到百骑了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.17,0:26:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}半年前 我率七十万大军出征
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.12,0:26:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到如今 却不到百骑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.33,0:26:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罢 罢 罢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.14,0:26:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}苍天助曹不助袁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.01,0:26:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 父帅 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.49,0:26:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 父帅 主公 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.91,0:27:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.01,0:27:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操用了许攸之计
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.85,0:27:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先是烧了乌巢的粮草辎重
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.85,0:27:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后又攻取了袁军的官渡大营
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.75,0:27:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁军一败 再败
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.16,0:27:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}百里战场 血流成河 尸骨成堆
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.66,0:27:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}七十万袁军 不剩百骑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.66,0:27:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}据说 已经逃回冀州了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.87,0:27:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}七十万大军所剩不足百骑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.07,0:27:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.07,0:27:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可曾听过这等奇闻
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.81,0:27:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁本初本是首屈一指的霸主
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.02,0:28:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}转眼之间 竟沦落为残寇
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.56,0:28:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操极善用兵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.16,0:28:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕冀州城
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.86,0:28:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不久会被他攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.00,0:28:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.50,0:28:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既是奸贼 又是雄主
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.21,0:28:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是兵家
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.51,0:28:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与此人同世
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.81,0:28:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不知幸也不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.35,0:28:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们兵不过三千
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.98,0:28:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又无坚可守
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.62,0:28:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此地不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.05,0:28:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 我原想投奔荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.86,0:28:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与刘表联手 举兵杭曹
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.76,0:28:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是现在袁绍七十万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.86,0:28:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}几乎丧尽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.43,0:28:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不知道刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.00,0:28:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有没有抗曹的胆识了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.87,0:28:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘表拥兵三十万
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.44,0:28:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其是他的荆州水兵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.58,0:28:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}号称天下无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.38,0:28:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他为什么要惧怕曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.31,0:29:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵多有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.65,0:29:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍的兵少吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.29,0:29:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}临敌胜败 首在统帅
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.56,0:29:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘表身为人主
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.16,0:29:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坐领荆襄九郡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.79,0:29:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十多年来却动也不动
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.60,0:29:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果他有二弟一小颗胆子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.63,0:29:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就不容曹操像今天这般放肆了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.00,0:29:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这刘表既然没有胆识
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.17,0:29:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那主公准备投何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.04,0:29:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘表虽无胆识
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.68,0:29:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但毕竟是贤良方正之主
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.05,0:29:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是皇氏宗族
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.99,0:29:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想当下之计
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.99,0:29:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也只能暂投刘表 徐图后举
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.03,0:29:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过这需要有一位大胆善言之人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.00,0:29:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先去探一探刘表的口风
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.66,0:29:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看看人家愿不愿意收容我们
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.57,0:30:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 在下愿意出使荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.65,0:30:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 孙乾愿往 再合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.98,0:30:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.40,0:30:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}参军孙乾 奉主公之命拜见明公
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.87,0:30:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 请起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.91,0:30:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢明公
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.78,0:30:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听说刘备仍然健在人间
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.55,0:30:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我深感欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.35,0:30:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如今在中原大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.35,0:30:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能够逃出曹孟德虎口的英雄豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.06,0:30:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经为数不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.73,0:30:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公说得极是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.50,0:30:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我主 不仅逃出了曹操的虎口
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.10,0:30:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且还要与虎相搏
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.97,0:31:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备起兵多年 屡战屡败
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.04,0:31:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕不是曹操的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.91,0:31:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与其说屡战屡败
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.91,0:31:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如说屡败屡战
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.65,0:31:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要我主一息尚存
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.62,0:31:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}誓必要扫除逆贼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.28,0:31:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}匡扶汉室
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.32,0:31:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公也是皇亲后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.22,0:31:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身上也流淌着高祖的鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.93,0:31:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公对我主的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.10,0:31:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不以为然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.46,0:31:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可敬可佩
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.90,0:31:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备差你来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.90,0:31:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是要借兵 借粮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.51,0:31:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是要 借城池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.75,0:31:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我主对明公一无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.28,0:31:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只想相助明公
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.82,0:31:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}助我 怎样助我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.32,0:32:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公 汉贼不两立 王业不偏安哪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.23,0:32:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操决不甘心做一个丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.06,0:32:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他志在篡汉自立
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.80,0:32:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍兵败后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.50,0:32:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操的下一个战略目标就是荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.87,0:32:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公大敌当前 战祸不远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.68,0:32:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀明公 我主兵马虽不多
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.05,0:32:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是愿意率领关羽 张飞 赵云
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.25,0:32:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三位当世勇猛豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.32,0:32:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在曹操来犯之时
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.82,0:32:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做明公的先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.22,0:32:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}助明公灭曹贼 成大业 安天下
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.99,0:32:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备和我同是皇室后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.70,0:32:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在这乱世之时
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.46,0:32:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们更应该相互扶持
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.50,0:32:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}共赴国难才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.67,0:32:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你告诉刘备 就说
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.94,0:32:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.45,0:32:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.92,0:32:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你先下去歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.12,0:33:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待会儿我让刘琦为你摆酒洗尘
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.12,0:33:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下告退
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.53,0:33:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有话就说
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.77,0:33:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 刘备是个灾星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.00,0:33:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备现在兵微将寡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.71,0:33:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无一座州郡可供他立足
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.67,0:33:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又惨遭曹操追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.58,0:33:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是在走投无路之下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.68,0:33:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才到主公这来求个存身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.55,0:33:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 我们万万不可被他利用
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.25,0:33:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果依你 怎么办才算妥当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.16,0:33:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眼下曹操势力滔天
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.76,0:33:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无人可敌
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.33,0:33:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但他对刘备却恨之入骨
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.26,0:33:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们不如斩了使者
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.86,0:33:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将首级送给曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.70,0:33:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以表明主公拒刘和曹之意
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.37,0:33:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此一来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.47,0:33:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操定然欢喜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.10,0:33:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也绝不会向荆州发兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.61,0:33:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.28,0:33:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.21,0:34:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿认为蔡将军所言 误国误主
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.05,0:34:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早晚会断送荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.65,0:34:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子言过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.59,0:34:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅与刘备同为皇亲帝胄
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.42,0:34:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}血脉相连
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.76,0:34:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如今刘备势穷来投
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.33,0:34:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要与父帅共敌曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.69,0:34:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们完全可以引为荆州之助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.93,0:34:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但父帅竟要把来使给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.70,0:34:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这事要是传扬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.84,0:34:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世人如何看待父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.74,0:34:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅又如何立足于天下呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.28,0:34:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备投吕布 则吕布亡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.64,0:34:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}投袁绍 则袁绍败
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.38,0:34:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前车之鉴 后事之师
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.71,0:34:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公千万三思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.08,0:34:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蔡将军言过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.52,0:34:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布智小 性贪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.89,0:34:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍贤愚不分 虚有其名
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.12,0:34:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕 袁都是败给曹操而不是刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.26,0:34:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.09,0:34:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我父帅又不是吕布 袁绍等人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.96,0:34:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅非但不会被刘备所用
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.37,0:34:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相反却能用刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.03,0:34:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.90,0:34:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.87,0:35:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 让孙乾上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.88,0:35:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙乾上堂
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.67,0:35:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙乾哪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.93,0:35:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看 我这里有个盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.51,0:35:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原先是装茶叶用的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.01,0:35:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在有人建议我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.81,0:35:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}取下你的头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.38,0:35:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}装在这个盒子里献与曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.02,0:35:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以表明我拒刘和曹之意
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.35,0:35:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保荆州太平
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.59,0:35:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你 觉着这个主意怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.93,0:35:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.30,0:36:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在砍下这颗头颅之前
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.17,0:36:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还在征求这个头颅的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.04,0:36:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真可谓是贤明之君哪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.07,0:36:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.91,0:36:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兼听则明嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.61,0:36:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我总是不耻下问的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.88,0:36:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果在下这颗头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.65,0:36:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能够换得荆州的太平
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那太值了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.12,0:36:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下也建议明公砍了去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.32,0:36:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是 曹操何许人也
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.36,0:36:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操能为这区区薄礼而动心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.23,0:36:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果在下是曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.16,0:36:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到这颗头颅一定会开怀大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.34,0:36:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还没向荆州用兵
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.17,0:36:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘景升就吓得送颗人头来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.21,0:36:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我挥师东进
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.18,0:36:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘景升还不吓得开城乞降吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.21,0:36:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果曹操准备明年攻打荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.15,0:36:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下的人头一到
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.49,0:36:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操定会提前攻取荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.12,0:36:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}砍了在下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.32,0:36:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非但保不住荆州的太平
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.16,0:36:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且会引祸上身
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.96,0:37:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公 你用一颗头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.60,0:37:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}换来两个强敌呀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.10,0:37:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 那第二个强敌是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.91,0:37:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公怎会不知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.67,0:37:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是我主刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.98,0:37:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你杀了刘备特意派来联谊的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.75,0:37:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他在众人面前饱受耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.82,0:37:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}痛不可当
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.85,0:37:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}试问明公
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.72,0:37:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备不会和你拼命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.99,0:37:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想不到 刘备在流亡之中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.80,0:37:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身边还跟随着你这样的义士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.93,0:37:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我主刘备身边义士众多
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.90,0:37:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}除了关羽 张飞 赵云之外
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.24,0:37:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有周仓 糜方 简雍等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.68,0:37:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么也得数到五十位之后
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.48,0:37:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才能数到我区区孙乾
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.45,0:37:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回刘皇叔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.52,0:38:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请他尽快来荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.42,0:38:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会大排仪仗 出城相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.66,0:38:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下领命
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.05,0:38:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}屡败之将刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.68,0:38:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}深谢景升皇兄收容之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.85,0:38:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德呀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.88,0:38:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你贤名扬天下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.72,0:38:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是仰幕已久
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.52,0:38:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今日起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.89,0:38:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}景升兄有何差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.02,0:38:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德定当效命
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.83,0:38:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不敢当 不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.90,0:38:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 我与你介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.10,0:38:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是长子刘琦 次子刘踪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.84,0:38:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜见刘皇叔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.90,0:38:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是英雄出少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.71,0:38:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}景升兄这两位龙虎公子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.81,0:38:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实在是让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.48,0:38:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊 请入城
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.58,0:38:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公请
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.35,0:39:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.55,0:39:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五年多来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.92,0:39:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刘备可以说是日夜不宁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.49,0:39:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每念及天子密授血诏
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.29,0:39:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都有如万箭穿心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.06,0:39:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}痛不可当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.20,0:39:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刘备上不能承天扶汉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.06,0:39:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下不能手刃奸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.43,0:39:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然是东征西讨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.47,0:39:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却是屡战屡败
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.17,0:39:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愧对天子 愧对苍生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.54,0:39:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤弟志大
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.88,0:39:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然就有天大的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.95,0:39:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愚兄志小
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.75,0:39:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此也就牵挂也少
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.49,0:39:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只想独守一隅
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.59,0:39:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保荆州太平
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.16,0:39:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恕在下直言
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.46,0:39:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操是个百年不遇的奸雄
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.83,0:39:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其权谋 兵略 淫威 霸术
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.17,0:40:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}俱可以说又狠又毒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.31,0:40:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自挟天子令诸侯开始
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.71,0:40:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}篡汉自立的野心可谓路人皆知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.05,0:40:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公乃汉皇后裔 世受国恩
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.49,0:40:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂能坐视曹贼篡国呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更何况 曹操他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.86,0:40:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早就对荆州垂涎三尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.80,0:40:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下一步 定会向荆州用兵
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.13,0:40:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依你所料 我应该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.84,0:40:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}高擎王旗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.74,0:40:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}召集天下志士 举兵伐曹
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.91,0:40:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只怕 现在时机还不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.18,0:40:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公 你正逢其时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.19,0:40:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍虽然兵败
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.22,0:40:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但有如百足大虫 死而不僵
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.39,0:40:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他手下仍有残兵二 三十万
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.60,0:40:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雄踞在冀 青 幽等州
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.87,0:41:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}图谋东山再起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.47,0:41:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操想根除袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.17,0:41:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时正在攻打冀州
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.17,0:41:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}战事正酣
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.61,0:41:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我料
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.54,0:41:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不到半年至一年的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.34,0:41:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他根本无法彻底消灭袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.51,0:41:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公此时你若率一支劲旅
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.08,0:41:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奔袭曹操首府许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.32,0:41:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定可大获成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.46,0:41:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奔赴许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.19,0:41:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.46,0:41:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我把话跟你说明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.33,0:41:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经年过六旬
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.97,0:41:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既无在诸侯中称霸之志
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.61,0:41:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更没有争夺天下之心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.98,0:41:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我主掌荆襄九郡之地
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.62,0:41:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经有十几年了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.15,0:41:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里的一草一木 一山一水
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.86,0:41:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一村一镇 一兵一民
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.19,0:42:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是我苦心栽培出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.43,0:42:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荆州背倚群山 足踏长江
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.60,0:42:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甲士三十万 战船五千艘
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.64,0:42:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我握有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.48,0:42:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坚守一方太平足矣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.72,0:42:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操 凭他那北方战骑
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.65,0:42:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}休想灭我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.06,0:42:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我靠我的水军战船
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.86,0:42:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也灭不了曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.03,0:42:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此 双方都应该明智一些
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.60,0:42:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听了明公这一番话
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.07,0:42:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下十分欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.98,0:42:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请尽此盅 以表敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.58,0:43:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我虽然没有争夺天下之心
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.05,0:43:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却真心实意地想要倚重于你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.36,0:43:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请明公吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.30,0:43:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管曹操是否真向荆州用兵
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.83,0:43:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都要做好御敌的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.44,0:43:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想拨出一座城池
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.44,0:43:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}名叫新野 供你驻军
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.08,0:43:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帮助我共拒曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.48,0:43:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凭你那关 张 赵三员虎将
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.99,0:43:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}足可令曹军丧胆哪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.73,0:43:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然了 你需要的军械粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.93,0:43:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全由我供给 行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.87,0:43:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下遵命
